{"tid":2479591,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"愛国僑領在巴西遭槍殺  中国領事館：性質惡劣 強烈譴責","createTime":"2021-04-08T02:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-08T02:20:09.000Z","uid":184679,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"09fa11dd8533d8d5ef7dc1136fee11f802070ba0","tid":2479591,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T02:07:56.000Z","msg":"巴西著名僑領、巴西華人協會會長張偉，昨日在巴西最大城市聖保羅一公園遭槍擊，當場身亡。中國駐聖保羅總領館嚴厲譴責犯罪行為，要求巴西警方從速破案。<br />\n<br />\n據中新社消息，張偉於4月6日在聖保羅市一公園晨練時遭槍擊喪身，中國駐聖保羅總領館第一時間向當地警方了解案情，總領館領導向警方高層提出交涉，敦促警方從速破案，早日將犯罪分子繩之以法。<br />\n<br />\n1968年出生於浙江溫州的張偉，1996年到巴西經商，在巴西經營有購物中心、中餐館等，2016年投資建設聖保羅「中拉合作園區」，助力中國「一帶一路」建設項目與拉美合作項目的對接。<br />\n<br />\n他歷任巴西溫州同鄉聯誼會會長、巴西中國商會會長和巴西華人協會會長。據稱，張偉在當地有相當影響力，曾協助多名遭綁架華人安全獲救。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/9b7f5e07ad83cd1c3aec3b189d9edf68/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210407/_2021040721542635415.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F9b7f5e07ad83cd1c3aec3b189d9edf68%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210407%2F_2021040721542635415.jpg&h=c47a4397&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline. com/news/realtime/chi/2041458</code></pre>"},{"pid":"4ef6ff5deb71a639dbecf5e866fc079c370f1467","tid":2479591,"uid":77580,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T02:08:31.000Z","msg":"出兵未，吳京在哪兒"},{"pid":"8c926c0347178f2902fdc19e85f9fbfff38e4f65","tid":2479591,"uid":144626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T02:08:48.000Z","msg":"去見毛主席啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034094b3c0872c11656b58daa8eee143be843ba2","tid":2479591,"uid":168138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T02:09:00.000Z","msg":"落去見毛主席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602b2b2395452aafa9e991